        <!-- Account Management -->
        <h2 class="text-info" id="account-management"><b>Account Management</b></h2>

        <h3 class="my-3" id="account-management-create-account"><b>1. How to create an account?</b></h3>
        <p>To create an account, click on the "Sign Up" button on the homepage, fill in your details, and follow the on-screen instructions to verify your email address.</p>

        <h3 class="my-3" id="account-management-reset-password"><b>2. How to reset your password?</b></h3>
        <p>If you forgot your password, click on "Forgot Password" on the login page, enter your email address, and follow the instructions sent to your email to reset your password.</p>

        <h3 class="my-3" id="account-management-delete-account"><b>3. How to delete your account?</b></h3>
        <p>To delete your account, go to your profile settings, select "Delete Account", and confirm your decision. Please note that this action is irreversible.</p>

        <h3 class="my-3" id="account-management-upgrade-account"><b>4. How to upgrade your account?</b></h3>
        <p>If you wish to upgrade your account for additional features, go to the "Upgrade Account" section in your profile settings and follow the instructions.</p>

        <hr class="bg-danger border-2 border-top border-dark" />

