        <h3 class="my-3" id="administration-create-tags"><b>1. How to create tags?</b></h3>
        <p>Administrators can create tags by going to the "Admin" panel, selecting "Manage Tags", and adding new tags as needed.</p>

        <h3 class="my-3" id="administration-manage-users"><b>2. How to manage users?</b></h3>
        <p>Administrators can manage users by accessing the "Admin" panel, selecting "User Management", and performing actions such as suspending, deleting, or upgrading user accounts.</p>

        <h3 class="my-3" id="administration-suspend-notes"><b>3. How to suspend notes?</b></h3>
        <p>To suspend a note, administrators should go to the "Admin" panel, select "Manage Notes", find the note in question, and click on "Suspend".</p>

